{"tid":506733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"孫政才沉迷《王者榮耀》  「一局不結束不下車」","createTime":"2017-12-22T13:31:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-22T14:34:17.000Z","uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d12a565c765e65a9d29a81a77ae8ea6fe41a43c1","tid":506733,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T13:31:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171218/57598273\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171218%2F57598273&d=x8fEFdSWgu6iV410OBY5YgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=ff0425cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171218%2F57598273&h=3400e61d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171218/57598273</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171218/large/1513596059_dd6b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171218%2Flarge%2F1513596059_dd6b.jpg&h=5323c6f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n重慶市委原書記孫政才自落馬以來，一直受到媒體關注，外界對其犯案內幕尤為感興趣。網絡最新傳聞指，孫政才不顧工作，沉迷網絡遊戲《王者榮耀》，曾多次在工作會議開始前打機，「一局不結束不下車」。<br />\n<br />\n12月15日，陳敏爾執掌的重慶官方對孫政才案作出最新表述，稱要「堅決清除孫政才惡劣影響」。新華社通報孫政才落馬罪名，包括「政治腐敗」、「經濟腐敗」、「生活腐敗」等。其中，通報還指出孫政才「嚴重違反工作紀律，官僚主義嚴重，慵懶無為」。<br />\n<br />\n孫政才「慵懶無為」，被指不顧工作，沉迷網絡遊戲。近期，中國網絡消息披露，孫政才曾多次在工作會議開始前沉迷游戲，「一局不結束不下車&rdquo;，而&ldquo;車外十多個人乾等着」，有民眾譏諷「孫政才是沉迷《王者榮耀》級别最高的領導人」。 除慵懶無為外，孫政才還被指生活腐化墮落，貪戀女色，有媒體稱，孫政才主政重慶時，挪用「一帶一路」專項資金，供情婦使用。而他的多名情婦亦為其誕下多個私生子。"},{"pid":"176b8f14dc758148ee2efc6aa14c1ab43be299a2","tid":506733,"uid":104443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T13:59:13.000Z","msg":"沉迷玩樂，貪圖女色，挪用國庫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜唔係個個做得中共嘅高官都係咁㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實真實原因在於，被拉落馬嘅官多數都唔係習派嘅人，純粹中共政治黨爭嘅結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a6da5b88ae636908b5caeff7f6e8c3b5d33fe9","tid":506733,"uid":31017,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T14:06:56.000Z","msg":"呢d鄰國打飛機檄文<br />\n睇得多都悶喇<br />\n權鬥成王敗寇<br />\n依家寫周永康強姦九十歲老嫗隻豬都得喇"},{"pid":"0d2cf318e56bf2cffb504f51b5ba4b52fb1e148c","tid":506733,"uid":389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T14:08:15.000Z","msg":"同佢對打果啲咪又係政軍高層"},{"pid":"1208588046ff572eeeef45d0d72610982e368e59","tid":506733,"uid":81150,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T14:10:28.000Z","msg":"你話一個呀伯沉迷隻手機game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不如屈個盲既偷睇國家機密啦"},{"pid":"b3da82c34f0252a45a1bbad200b21b4a411f2d84","tid":506733,"uid":86587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T14:12:08.000Z","msg":"仲以為咁高地位嘅人咩都有，唔會鍾意打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0480a7b743990118c464fe520a45af4f86ae870","tid":506733,"uid":85819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T14:12:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f296e4cc26995a11acac7adb054bb62894db068","tid":506733,"uid":47492,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T14:34:17.000Z","msg":"推阿婆落海。強姦隻豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}